Edmund Pevensie is the third oldest Pevensie child, Edmund is a brat for most ofThe Lion, The Witch, and the Wardrobe.Edmund is spiteful and mean, and likes to tease his sister, Lucy. His greed for the enchanted Turkish Delight leads him to act as a traitor against his siblings. Edmund joins forces with the White Witch, but eventually sees the error of his ways and returns to the good side.